Description: To everyone in this plant: / This plant is engaged / upon Government work / Every person here owes / The United States / a duty to do his utmost / to make material for / our ships carefully / and speedily.../ let us be your part / Our country is / depending on you / Emergency Fleet Corporation / Thomsen-Ellis Co.., Baltimore, New York
